The '''laser lasso''' was a children's toy. Similar in concept to a [[Lightwhip/Legends|lightwhip]], but in comparison non-lethal, the lasso emitted a "laser" that could wrap around objects and throw them about.

In [[18 BBY/Legends|18 BBY]], [[Lune Oddo Divinian|Lune Divinian]] used his laser lasso in conjunction with his untrained [[The Force/Legends|Force]] powers to direct a [[Discord missile/Legends|discord missile]] away from his companions.

